<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two fragments - not joining - from a text inscribed on several adjoining blocks. a: left side, a block chipped along left edge and damaged at the lower right corner (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.96</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.43</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.56</measure>). b right side,  a rectangular block (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.46</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.44</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.61</measure>) with an area cut away at the top left.</p>
</div>
